{"type": "article", "id": 33627, "title": "哄孩子入睡太累？这张床想替家长分担｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-10-23T23:08:38Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 8752, "name": "Lexon"}, {"id": 18678, "name": "Fuseproject"}, {"id": 21616, "name": "Bebop"}, {"id": 34207, "name": "Note Design"}, {"id": 34208, "name": "Zilenzio"}, {"id": 30214, "name": "Saif Faisal"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 221, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161023203443fpF1uNDEPzIylksa.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Wi-Wi bottle by Ajay Choudhary</h3><p>想要避免黏糊糊的油壶和台面上的油渍并不是什么容易的事情，如果你觉得自己倒油并没有那么精准的话，不妨试试 Ajay Choudhary 设计的 Wi-Wi 油壶。Choudhary 为瓶口设置了两道屏障：细长的出油管可以有效避免油一不小心倒多了的问题，让人更好把握；管子周围则额外设计了一个回收口，让多余的油滴能从这里流回瓶中，确保你不会再因为倒完油而满手粘腻。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161023184130OKlhgiXGRpPWeBzv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161023184130j4tYsDI9byk7RBZn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.677264\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610231841304XfZcwoDtQAOg73y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>Blossom 360 by BEBOP</h3><p>韩国的 <a href=\"http://bebopdesigners.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">BEBOP</a> 工作室想让你用一朵绽放的机械花放音乐。这个名叫 Blossom 360 的便携式音响是工作室提交给法国品牌 <a href=\"http://www.lexon-design.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lexon</a> 的一款概念设计作品，简约的圆柱体顶部包含一个凸起的圆锥形喇叭，使整个造型看起来像是花朵一样。喇叭可以按压后嵌入圆柱体中，携带起来相当方便。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161023191017M47xgyhqijU1m3of.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161023191017oZNVXiPC63OxvMt5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161023191017RBsOkASYFwd9feoG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161023191018jfZSXehU2rPT1Ylw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161023191018uVJMBG6WEmFrnOPA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016102319101739sw4ujNAYnm17B2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.732274\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>Auxillite by Auxillite team</h3><p>iPhone 7/7 Plus 取消了 3.5mm 耳机接口，对于很多用户来说，没办法同时充电听音乐成了一大苦恼。一个美国设计团队因此带来了这款名为 Auxillite 的外设产品：它实际上是一个非常小巧便携的适配器，两侧分别提供了 Lightning 和 3.5mm 接口。除了普通版之外，设计团队还研发了 Auxillite S，在原有基础上新增了一个可以摆放手机的底座，同时还能当绕线器使用。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1478028788/auxillite-lightest-2-in-1-dac-converter-for-your-i\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，两种版本的最低价分别为 13 和 17 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161023193251MAobYl8s1ucfyT5E.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.317647\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610231932513eUQHmIiBPTAEgOV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.992582\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161023193252tYkTuGB9gjI8oeHD.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.754412\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161023193251W1wqyom2LjMHAeiT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.772581\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>Snoo by Fuseproject &amp; Dr. Harvey Karp</h3><p>作为四个孩子的父亲，世界上首个智能摇篮 <a href=\"https://www.happiestbaby.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Snoo</a> 的设计师 Yves Behar 对哄婴儿导致自己一夜未眠深有体会。Snoo 由 Behar 的 <a href=\"https://fuseproject.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">fuseproject</a> 工作室和儿科医生 Harvey Karp 花费四年多时间共同研发，一旦检测到婴儿的哭声就会自动开始晃动，模拟家长的怀抱。大部分婴儿能够在一分钟之内入睡，如果超出时间，配套的手机应用会提醒家长孩子可能是饿了或是需要替换尿布。为了安全，Snoo 还配备了可以在五秒完成组装的固定用襁褓，防止婴儿在晃动时移动。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610232003255FYdbVqTkRK1GtgQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.746667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161023200325qXLlenJdbFED72Py.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.751667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161023200329b2tAwpQ48asi3JF5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161023200325XcyHu3QoVmwGFWSf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.786667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>Focus divider by Note Design</h3><p>在开放式的办公空间，屏风对塑造员工私密、安静的工作环境相当重要，然而对于没有固定位置的人来说，一个很难根据需要进行调节的大屏风并不能满足需求。瑞典的 <a href=\"http://notedesignstudio.se/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Note Design</a> 最近为屏风品牌 <a href=\"http://www.zilenzio.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Zilenzio</a> 设计了一套名为 Focus 的产品，可以根据需要随意调整它的大小。除此之外，还提供了多种尺寸可选，既有落地的大屏风，也有能放在桌上的小巧款式。这套屏风即将在今年科隆的 ORGAREC 办公家具展上亮相。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161023201417NuPzASI39nwjQHM0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713615\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610232014178QDP4JOxFkgleSMb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714789\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610232014173OZUK0LJaWMo8PAH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714789\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161023201417h7oVwSyaEj68mWMb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713615\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161023201417JdnPUg3IsZfFzSR6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714789\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610232014170vus7c4KVFkE8JUP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713615\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>Alfredo lamp by Saif Faisal</h3><p>简洁利落的轮廓和隐藏在顶部的光源，由 <a href=\"http://www.saif-faisal.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Saif Faisal</a> 设计的 <a href=\"http://www.saif-faisal.com/alfredo-lamp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Alfredo</a> 属于那种可以很好地融入环境当中的台灯。看起来很像是一件木雕装饰物的它并不会给人一种张扬的感觉，打开后柔和的灯光会映照在底座和“灯柱”的部分，很适合放在床头柜用作阅读灯使用。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610232031281suPIofyTYOwHqAx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.146667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161023203128M1G5uV7a8pnwoB3Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.737500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161023203128mKA6FbsuiIYfyhPn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.068333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610232031297CZ0fKsh9npNlE1v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.408333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161023203128q2Ijp6dBX09JV5hH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.088333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}